  "Her back and knees hurt.",
  "And now … She glanced at her wristwatch.",
  "They were going to go swimming at some Officers’ Club … at 1300 hours on their only day off in two weeks?",
  "",
  "Ethel yanked the covers back, revealing Frankie in her T-shirt and panties.",
  "She wore socks to bed, even in this heat, to save her toes from bugs and other creepy crawlers.",
