  "They were not the words she wanted to hear from him.",
  "“I’ve already had my heart broken over here,” she said quietly, taking another step back.",
  "“And I expect an officer to be a gentleman, Rye.”",
  "",
  "He locked his hands behind his back.",
  "Soldier’s stance.",
  "A respectful distance.",
  "“Forgive me for coming here tonight.”",
  "His voice had a rough edge to it.",
  "“It wasn’t my place.”",
  "",
  "She nodded, tried again to smile.",
  "“Stay alive, Rye.",
  "I’m seeing too many bird pilots in my OR.”",
  "",
  "“Goodbye, Frankie.”",
  "",
  "“Goodbye.”",
  "",
