  "The Quonset hut shook, IVs rattled in their holders.",
  "Her helmet kept clanking down onto the bridge of her nose.",
  "",
  "Another hit.",
  "Close.",
  "",
  "In the OR, the wounded who were able rolled off their beds or litters and hit the floor, their IVs yanked out of their veins.",
