  "Frankie followed her new boss down the hallway, past half a series of closed doors.",
  "She was shown the restrooms, the lab, the equipment room; they ended up back on the first floor at the nurses’ station.",
  "",
  "“Sit there,” Mrs. Henderson said.",
  "“Answer the phone.",
  "If there’s trouble, page me.”",
  "",
  "Frankie took a seat.",
  "You may help patients to the restroom, refill their water, change bedpans.",
