  "Me.",
  "On the night shift.",
  "",
  "The only good thing is the anger sometimes makes me forget how sad I am.",
  "",
  "I’ll stick with it, though.",
  "Prove myself.",
  "I’ll bet you’re thinking of my first shift in-country.",
  "",
  "I’ve got this.",
  "Thanks for reminding me, by the way.",
  "I still love nursing.",
  "",
  "That’s something.",
  "",
  "So, how’s life on the horse farm?",
  "Still kicking ass in your classes?",
