  "",
  "May 14, 1971",
  "",
  "Dear Frankie,",
  "",
  "You’re breaking up the band, girl, and I hate it, but I think it’s time, and this is the kick in the ass I needed.",
  "I’ve sent a résumé to Operation Breadbasket in Atlanta.",
  "Maybe I’ll meet Jesse Jackson!",
  "",
  "I’ll miss you!",
  "",
  "Keep in touch.",
  "",
  "Stay cool,",
  "",
  "B",
  "",
  "PS: I’ll bet Noah pops the question to Ethel now that we are out of the way.",
